{"tid":721882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【丟架】強國女清真寺熱舞 網民鬧爆「腦殘」：喺中東早被打死！","createTime":"2018-06-29T04:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T05:59:47.000Z","uid":153600,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0b7a4c271bbdad0b953d4a2e2341854fd42e53","tid":721882,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"兩名中國女遊客，上周六（23日）身穿熱褲，在馬來西亞沙巴亞庇市水上清真寺的圍牆上，大跳熱舞拍片，引發當地人不滿，兩人被捕後罰款，並被遣返回國。消息傳回內地後，網民狂轟兩女「腦殘」、「想紅想瘋了」，更批評兩人出國前都不好好做功課、不尊重別人宗教，幸好事發在大馬，「要是在中東的清真寺，早就被打死了」"},{"pid":"8d8cae1d456739fcca238eb89182433793edb114","tid":721882,"uid":126567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"抖音真係毒藥黎<br />\n玩到班痴咗線既人更加痴線"},{"pid":"a7ffc72447b1af76f924c2dfed529d6bba8fe2a7","tid":721882,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"低啦"},{"pid":"786974b1d89315105e0fcecb9929caed90f290b0","tid":721882,"uid":182758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"唔洗比面伊斯蘭狗"},{"pid":"68eb8fb824d363e58e8b88a5b793353c5d10845f","tid":721882,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"可能習慣咗喺中國清真寺跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285290c10770c89040568720983fdef5fa5efe30","tid":721882,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"玩抖音會弱智定弱智先玩抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a56ccf8e3293eef6869046275d9232f727d1b5","tid":721882,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"係中東分分鐘拉人合法處決"},{"pid":"ed5a3e6289670f688a148642e32503cfaab67faf","tid":721882,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8a56ccf8e3293eef6869046275d9232f727d1b5","tid":721882,"uid":59567,"like":0,"disl